# Local `npm run dev`: leave VITE_API_BASE_URL unset so `/api/*` proxies to localhost:8000.
# Remote API from local UI (optional):
#   Staging:    VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://kycautomation-staging.up.railway.app
#   Production: VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://kycautomation-production.up.railway.app
# Cloud deploy builds use `.env.staging` or `.env.production` instead.